y theorist but it happened one month after she got vaccinated in 2021. Now she's pretty much crippled for life. 100% it was caused by the vaccine. Her doctor said he doesn't know how it happened it just happens. I don't know why we're letting these ghouls get off for what they did the untold pain that this shit shot caused.  Not everybody went willingly. Everyone was told it was safe and effective.  This isn't a conspiracy theory anymore it's 100% fact vac cine injuries and death from the covid shot is real where is the accountability. Fucking criminal cowards you're gonna burn in hell for what you did to people if you don't get accountability here on earth you will.  Congressman and senators of pieces of greedy fucking shit. Is this was real America we would have been marching on Washington years ago for what they did.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 8, "score_up": 51, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZfCf68I", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 326, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8598082, "raw_content": "", "author": "salbro", "created": 1777873958231, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "DrumOctopus", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.patriots.win", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZfCf68I.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.patriots.win/post/JmLcUXE1MLSk.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/azEsOFEwKnnbPnW6.png", "width": 768, "content-type": "png", "height": 723}], "blurh